{"lastModified":1761558808103,"uri":"c::10923570597::vessel::36239510-df3f-11ef-aca5-71e1b7961b18","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Indonesia\n\nSet sail aboard Lamain Voyages I, a luxurious Phinisi built in 2020, and embark on an unforgettable escapade through the heart of Komodo National Park. Immerse yourself in paradise as turquoise waters lap against the hull, and diverse landscapes unfold before you. Explore volcanic islands, pristine beaches teeming with life, and vibrant coral reefs teeming with colorful fish. Witness the awe-inspiring presence of Komodo dragons, graceful manta rays gliding through the crystal-clear depths, and the spectacle of thousands of bats taking flight at sunset.\n\nUnwind in one of 6 elegant cabins, each boasting an en-suite bathroom for your comfort. Savor delicious meals in the spacious dining room and toast to unforgettable moments at the bar. Adventure awaits, whether you choose to dive into the underwater world, hike through lush landscapes, or snorkel alongside vibrant marine life. Tailor the itinerary to your desires, from thrilling activities to moments of serene relaxation on the expansive top deck, where panoramic views and refreshing breezes await. Sip on complimentary non-alcoholic drinks and snacks as you lose yourself in the beauty of the surroundings.\n\nThis isn’t just a trip; it’s an experience crafted for you. With a maximum capacity of 16 guests, enjoy personalized attention and intimate encounters with the wonders of Komodo. From witnessing Komodo dragons in their natural habitat to creating memories that will last a lifetime, Lamain Voyages I is your gateway to paradise. Contact them today and start planning your unforgettable Indonesian adventure!","blueprint":{"name":"LAMAIN I","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::36239510-df3f-11ef-aca5-71e1b7961b18::assets::56b3bc30-df42-11ef-9908-af7f5c675be6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::36239510-df3f-11ef-aca5-71e1b7961b18::as